12. AI Intelligence Layer
12.1 Overview

The AI Intelligence Layer is the core differentiator of the platform. Unlike traditional GitHub analyzers that aggregate metrics, this layer transforms raw GitHub data into evidence-backed engineering insights.

Design Principles
AI should infer, not hallucinate.
Every insight should reference observable GitHub evidence.
Recommendations should be actionable.
AI outputs should be deterministic where possible.
Expensive analyses should be cached.
