13. AI Orchestrator
Purpose

The AI Orchestrator coordinates all AI modules and determines:

Which analyses are required
Execution order
Parallel processing opportunities
Prompt selection
Result aggregation
Cost optimization

The orchestrator never analyzes data itself. It delegates work to specialized engines.

