24. AI Safety & Reliability

The platform must:

Never fabricate skills.
Cite repository evidence for conclusions.
Mark uncertain inferences with confidence levels.
Avoid making claims about a developer that cannot be supported by GitHub data.
Allow users to regenerate reports after profile updates.
